<br />
classes.
<br />

<br />
Any thoughts which of the two would be more fun to just screw around with?
<br />

<br />
I'll probably also use him down the road to do tradeskills, assuming that 
<br />
Gnome enchanters are still way overbalanced for that.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
