				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I read the thought about breeze and yes it might be work, but if I keep all the casters in a group up with breeze, they almost never run below half mana. Add this to a couple of summoners and wizards along with the healer and you are pulling non stop. Having breeze keep the healers and casters up on mana makes it very nice for the tank as he doesnt take as much damage and pulls much faster. I always try to keep a bit of mana in reserve for adds which happen even before lvl 20. If you think of breeze as a not needed except in rare occasions spell let your casters run out of mana and you have none to cast breeze on them before the combat is done, watch your mana regen during combat with it on and without it and then say again that the spell is only work.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
